151
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,800
before you gave me

152
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:59,320
a detailed plan
of the information flow interface.

153
00:09:59,521 --> 00:10:01,001
So I thought,

154
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,560
your talent was as good as your looks,

155
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,161
so we'd make a good couple.

156
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,840
Watch your words.

157
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,921
You're making us
engineering students turn red,

158
00:10:10,921 --> 00:10:11,921
okay?

159
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,521
Shall we...

160
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,560
talk about money?

161
00:10:26,121 --> 00:10:27,480
Did the professor tell you?

162
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,361
When Mr. Zhang called me,

163
00:10:30,361 --> 00:10:32,401
He wished I could beat around the bush.

164
00:10:33,881 --> 00:10:35,720
Are you facing any difficulties?

165
00:10:37,121 --> 00:10:38,041
Or...

166
00:10:38,241 --> 00:10:39,401
