167
00:10:40,121 --> 00:10:40,840
By the way,

168
00:10:41,241 --> 00:10:42,001
I remember

169
00:10:42,001 --> 00:10:43,521
after you answered a call
from your family,

170
00:10:43,881 --> 00:10:45,560
