220
00:13:03,241 --> 00:13:04,921
Shen Jing should be up by now.

221
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,641
By the way.

222
00:13:07,241 --> 00:13:08,361
How's it going

223
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:10,161
