224
00:13:11,761 --> 00:13:12,921
Nothing.

225
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,521
She has a junior

226
00:13:16,521 --> 00:13:17,800
whom she'd like to introduce to you.

227
00:13:19,281 --> 00:13:20,200
Last time she saw

228
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,361
our group photo

229
00:13:21,881 --> 00:13:23,800
and asked if you have a girlfriend.

230
00:13:25,001 --> 00:13:26,361
You're so good-looking,

231
00:13:26,361 --> 00:13:27,881
