239
00:13:55,401 --> 00:13:56,560
Recently...

240
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,881
I met

241
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:00,560
a girl.

242
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:07,921
She's quite clever,

243
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,761
a little mischievous,

244
00:14:26,641 --> 00:14:27,761
and receptive.

245
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:29,560
That's great.

246
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,281
You met her on vacation?

247
00:14:31,680 --> 00:14:32,440
No.

248
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,121
We're from the same high school.

249
00:14:34,401 --> 00:14:35,401
From the same high school?

250
00:14:35,761 --> 00:14:37,080
Why are you dating with her only now?

251
00:14:39,241 --> 00:14:40,361
Back then,

252
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:42,080
