253
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:45,680
So I didn't date her.

254
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,080
You're kidding me.

255
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:50,440
Is it because she doesn't like you?

256
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,361
But I don't think so.

257
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,200
You still got it.

258
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:15,080
It's locked.

259
00:15:29,881 --> 00:15:31,080
Not a soul in sight.

260
00:15:31,521 --> 00:15:32,600
Maybe they're busy.

261
00:15:33,161 --> 00:15:34,001
Just keep waiting.

262
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,281
In ten minutes,

263
00:15:39,921 --> 00:15:41,560
Shen Jing should be up from bed.

264
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:43,521
Then we'll call her,

265
00:15:43,521 --> 00:15:44,521
tell her I'm safe,

266
00:15:44,521 --> 00:15:45,720
so we don't have to go in.

267
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,921
Otherwise, once it gets warmer,

268
00:15:46,921 --> 00:15:48,320
I'll go out like a light.

269
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:51,881
Let's rest here for now.

270
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,641
(Yu Tu.)

271
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:18,361
(I hope)

272
